{"tid":1452070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"文宣意見，重點！","createTime":"2019-08-11T23:43:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T06:42:25.000Z","uid":56483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d9ea7f5c1085f77a97f7e6a753f7a87723bc526d","tid":1452070,"uid":56483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:43:31.000Z","msg":"昨晚最重要兩件事，必須要散出去全世界<br />\n<br />\n1. 葵芳站及太古站內放催淚彈<br />\n呢件事絕對係恐怖襲擊<br />\n室內用催淚彈呢種氣體化學武器<br />\n係徹底違反國際鎮暴使用催淚彈的合理做法<br />\n同當年東京沙林毒氣恐怖襲擊性質上完全冇分別！<br />\n<br />\n2. 太古站內近距離行刑式開槍、推示威者落電梯<br />\n呢啲完全係屠殺行為<br />\n<br />\n香港警察已經淪為恐怖組織<br />\n求國際介入人道救援"},{"pid":"102e2562bd339a9ba59e53c8beeec1a8600e5acc","tid":1452070,"uid":269515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:42:25.000Z","msg":"大家可唔可以整多少少人神共憤嘅俾遊客<br />\n好多時佢地知 Hong Kong fight for freedom<br />\n但好多時吸睛嘅係<span style=\"color: red;\">殘忍同無恥嘅行為</span><br />\n同埋可以出<span style=\"color: red;\">數字</span><br />\n吸引左佢地再講其他野<br />\n要令佢地覺得我地起<span style=\"color: red;\">人道災難</span>入面<br />\n佢地係於心不忍 而唔係其他國家嘅野唔關佢地事<br />\n<br />\n文宣小妹有野想講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1451498\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1451498</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">721元朗恐襲</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JUakSS6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJUakSS6.jpg&h=48c936c9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rEbzXjM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrEbzXjM.jpg&h=f7ef03d2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hgGzXjO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhgGzXjO.jpg&h=52ffb00e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rM2fGMt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrM2fGMt.jpg&h=9fcca1e6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yi0MOru.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%